The paper deals with the capacity of wireless channels, which is a topic that falls under the Information Theory (cs.IT) and Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the use of copula, which is a statistical tool used in Machine Learning (cs.MA) and Data Science (cs.DS). Additionally, the paper's focus on QoS assessment suggests that it could also be classified under the Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) sub-category.
